                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-179-off969 t18240916-179-crimeloc971"></join>. There were three ducks, one drake, and forty fowls, and next morning I missed two ducks, a fowl, and a pigeon, which had been all safe the night before, except the pigeon. I saw no more of them till my master brought them back.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I bought the duck and fowl on the road the over-night; I found the pigeon.</p>
